@NODE INTRO "Introduction"
@{B}
Introduction
@{UB}
Super Anagram Solver is a simple program which will find words out of
a given anagram very quickly by scanning the entire English dictionary
for any matches. This program is good for solving anagram puzzles found in
newspapers, magazines and puzzle books. It also helps you cheat at scrabble! 

@ENDNODE

@NODE USE "How to use the Super Anagram Solver"
@{B}
How to use Super Anagram Solver
@{UB}
@{I}Gadgets@{UI}

* At the top of the window is a text gad tool. This is where you type in
  the Anagram you wish to solve, or a word you wish to check.

* Start will start searching for words within the Anagram specified.

* Stop will stop searching.

* < and > scrolls up and down the words found. You can also use the scroll
  bar, or the cursor keys.

* 2 Chrs will find words out of the anagram which are two or more characters
  in size, and so on.

* Match Length will only find words which match the anagrams length.

* Check Word searches the English dictionary to see if the word is present.

* Use letters will cause Anagram Solver to only find words which contain   
  the characters specified.
@{I}
Menus
@{UI}
* Program, About, tells you that I made Anagram Solver!
* Program, Quit, exits from Anagram Solver.
* Options, Busy Bar, activates the busy bar, however this DOES slow down
  the searching operation.
* Options, Speak, Says each word that it finds.

@ENDNODE

