@NODE NOTES "Important Notes"
@{B}
Important Notes
@{UB}
There is a bug in the scroll bar of this program, which may crash your
system if you try to move the scroll bar when there are no words found. This problem could have been solved, however I lost the Anagram Solvers source code, when my hard drive went down.

